{"tid":2212952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆集中營翻版 路透：中國對西藏擴大「勞工培訓」計畫","createTime":"2020-09-22T07:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T13:35:14.000Z","uid":21141,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"190520deec7ece7400602b8642b23f85ed7c2237","tid":2212952,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"中國踐踏少數民族人權的案例再添一樁，據《路透》披露，中國正迫使越來越多的藏人離開農村，進入最近新建成、軍事化管理的「培訓中心」，從事低報酬的勞力工作，模式與新疆「再教育營」如出一轍，以改善貧窮為由，對大規模的人實行強制勞動。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，根據西藏自治區政府發布的消息，今年前7個月，已經有超過50萬人接受了培訓計畫，占西藏總人口的15％，其中有5萬人在西藏地區工作，並且有數千人被送至中國其他地區，這些人通常從事紡織、建築和農業的低報酬工作。"},{"pid":"f9bb08a4880615d6801503c5d60a4eefe70988b9","tid":2212952,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3299543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3299543&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=5b6eb123\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3299543&h=fa86b051\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3299543</a>"},{"pid":"c3a0f6a7525988d5ddf1c49ade7a378309c44c52","tid":2212952,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"slavery 2020"},{"pid":"322546e6fe757fcdeea68077ed60fecd95b90a0e","tid":2212952,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"西藏農奴制"},{"pid":"4c53cf06d18d3de7be1c44ba2efb5636cc379bfa","tid":2212952,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a5f9f485775d9a6a81c4aff9e3077030547d2d","tid":2212952,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"香